Distance units you can use when querying our server:

| Unit name | Shortcut |
|------|------------|
| Mile | `mi` or `miles` |
| Yard | `yd` or `yards` |
| Feet | `ft` or `feet` |
| Kilometer | `km` or `kilometers` |
| Meter | `m` or `meters` |
| Nautical mile | `NM`, `nmi` or `nauticalmiles` |
